{
  "blocks": [
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_b7559fb0e84953e11ff74898",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "假设我们的任务是在 React 中创建一个概念验证——一个允许用户添加、编辑和删除他们想做的任务的应用程序，并且在不删除任务的情况下将其标记为完成。这篇文章将引导你完成基本的 App 组件结构和样式，为以后添加的单个组件定义和交互性做好准备。",
        "text_hash": "5b6cb45aa55278efa858010f74983d04eb4ac49e520c377f40f4f7a0b45f5a2f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6c17718cb77972a9d92ce505",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "[!NOTE]\n如果你需要对照我们的版本检查你的代码，你可以在我们的 todo-react 仓库 中找到一个完成版本的 React 应用代码。关于运行中的实时版本，参见  .",
        "text_hash": "5b81f39107e0aeb2853a76b0c9125190c945fa14043657819aec5718bbee9fd9",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "quotation"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3fd4a3924b260d4fc7030e7a",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "条件：",
        "text_hash": "a26bfcbf7ac83a58f6458cd6a626af0220da03ec89d28a4bfff781916ac26766",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_04c20fc21815ee31619b12f3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "熟悉核心  HTML 、 CSS\n          和  JavaScript  语言，了解 终端/命令行 。",
        "text_hash": "20ee108d088053019336acfd2e231e8d705313fd4eff985f768bbfeda18817d2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_c6bea45895da08e11c9bd996",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "目标：",
        "text_hash": "4d2d25a2888d3e7c13db6b2e275e0179ab434807992666123db412d5f31e27a0",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_89f651c924d9024a30adbcf7",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "介绍我们待办清单的案例，并获得基本的  App  结构和样式。",
        "text_hash": "9030974f1a54fb121ac4e78ae4b851afb47d0ae073cc8482f219001d99fe526a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_f4dd51aef055e7a9f00ac191",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "用户故事",
        "text_hash": "5f778a4d80947b5ef859fcfb6f30e6038e8f98191da1f0f00e62fe956a5dc5a4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8bd5340b43d62a16431116c5",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "在软件开发中，用户故事是从用户的角度出发的一个可操作的目标。在我们开始工作之前，定义用户故事将帮助我们集中精力开展工作。我们的应用程序应该满足以下的故事：",
        "text_hash": "8a2ed19e7f2cbc41524c0c08347f81a7f30fd29fd25f140b525a19473930f57b",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_14fb8a4fdb6222b123845185",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "作为一名用户，我可以",
        "text_hash": "96de64513785b829888b9c90cda6d4a05fe6e32337ee5fe7264b4bc926090384",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_8ad93e799313a63c2eb163e1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "读取任务清单。\n使用鼠标或键盘，添加一个任务。\n使用鼠标或键盘，将任何任务标记为已完成。\n使用鼠标或键盘，删除任何任务。\n使用鼠标或键盘，编辑任何任务。\n查看一个特定的任务子集：所有的任务、仅活动中的任务，或只有已完成的任务。",
        "text_hash": "369fb6a2d30f1a222491f4d5d6195fa8ab7b5c1c46e0eff900f51be9c195cc1a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3b2a08cdfdc4518866bd651e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们将逐一处理这些故事。",
        "text_hash": "ac01e9be178a0b3d8b60aa1f8b246348b18484cd586d76031580051d4829746f",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_730b0bee8f93ca0896020688",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "开始前的清理",
        "text_hash": "10a45f34b1775756fdcb2f8f9c1fbfc201e929839b4405d73a22fd8f5b489e1e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_de05c62fc5079a61aacde5cd",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "create-react-app 添加了一些我们在项目中完全不会用到的文件。",
        "text_hash": "d515bfcf70e98929448992af29c2d0bebbe16fb3411e63e4d04312066c481ddc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6fb3cdaeb8a814b2c9258528",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们不打算写每个组件的样式表，所以首先从 App.js 的顶部删除 App.css 的导入。\n我们也不打算使用 logo.svg 文件，所以也要删除这个导入。",
        "text_hash": "0853c593a781531dfeb3d2327acda194dd37919d93e2b8e3eac8e05a036b12dc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1b0b8410da85b95e71a830d6",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "然后，复制并粘贴以下命令到你的终端，删除一些不需要的文件。确保你是在应用程序的根目录下开始的！",
        "text_hash": "cacf6d4dc1e054d83172c374e4a0036d7fa1c107c8fcd7badcb99ea8038b7c95",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_d56aa0fd34fbedfc739e861f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "bash\n# Move into the src directory of your project\ncd src\n# Delete a few files\nrm -- App.test.js App.css logo.svg serviceWorker.js setupTests.js\n# Move back up to the root of the project\ncd ..",
        "text_hash": "8d44cd6b9bae9df460e5c4a7fdaa1a93fe9fa4052f3d8f516ecf019a767c3fe4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_08f861a8e1c1f474bc53defb",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "注意：",
        "text_hash": "4c847838756576dfc94ae24814cfa40dfd36533332a256060bb04de51b1a0185",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
