      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_77b029000c18723f569d3e68",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "todo-matic app, unstyled, showing a jumbled mess of labels, inputs, and buttons",
        "text_hash": "538937fb710122622d90b06ac30e9dd73941c2133080f060cbed0fe1d43538ab",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_62a84cdf28d0f12cb367aaa3",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "它很难看，而且还没有功能，但这没关系——我们一会儿就会为它设计样式。首先，考虑一下我们的 JSX，以及它是如何与我们的用户故事相对应的。",
        "text_hash": "b1e9c4328166171743c05e0377e11ddc3f1fef92fde48a35e15baf9b81a1a59e",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_62212d04239102561ccb416b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "我们有一个   元素，有一个   用于写出一个新任务，还有一个按钮用于提交表单。\n我们有一组按钮，用于筛选我们的任务。\n我们有一个标题，用于告诉我们还有多少任务。\n我们有三个任务，安排在一个无序的列表中。每项任务都是一个列表项（ ），有编辑和删除的按钮，还有一个复选框可以将其勾选为完成。",
        "text_hash": "ee5e37c18aae9264d95550e9f672f4d8862bd60fe446e435d9d207281a370c5c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_5920de4eabb507fefd9be804",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这些表格将允许我们*添加*任务；按钮让我们可以对任务进行*筛选*；我们通过标题和列表*查看*任务。用于*编辑*任务的 UI 目前很缺乏。这没关系——我们以后再写。",
        "text_hash": "5a074db479a07152d65a7e3f1d709e963c633b60924aaa69377208b5a6c205a6",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_1d2fdec2fd8f9a1b80700cb9",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "无障碍功能",
        "text_hash": "63434d474d43107e2533a343a28d8681137cb37147866710a6e45b78c0ce1bc1",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_222e99e8e501c215d6f37dcc",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "你可能会注意到这里有一些不寻常的属性。比如说：",
        "text_hash": "b8c1fee40a1a805bdfb4dad06cc1e65f944e82760a21852d0834d49286d2f92a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_0f0c176a1420fa0702753913",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_607ec31760fa65f7e4cba0ad",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Show\n   all\n    tasks",
        "text_hash": "55640b88228743ffe5b4a5a1f6fc632814278ed973c62fb12a755b6c6c947c79",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_e49cfb5ca0ba54b06f13e57b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "这里的 aria-pressed 告诉辅助技术（比如屏幕阅读器），该按钮可以有两种状态。按压 或 未按压 。可以把它们看作 开 和 关 。设置为 true 意味着该按钮默认是被按下的。",
        "text_hash": "b3dce77af5d6ea816ee8a6b7cac323f841feb6e67fdf300011dbae08a237284c",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bec7c848ef7f821b74941e58",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "visually-hidden 这个类还没有效果，因为我们还没有包含任何 CSS。一旦我们把样式写好，任何带有这个类的元素都会被隐藏起来，视力正常的用户不会看到，而屏幕阅读器用户仍然可以使用——这是因为视力正常的用户不需要这些词；它们的存在是为了给没有额外视觉环境帮助的屏幕阅读器用户提供更多关于这个按钮的信息。",
        "text_hash": "27e56b65cea1b7e42ea25b06bccde7a3b1fee1256b100b0583030a7a0c1b3934",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_11e481370260da0e76e58412",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "再往下，你可以找到我们的   元素：",
        "text_hash": "f2dcb83cea175556226ee5446f9973598aee9c92d2767446a2eaf10d46dca942",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_24eebca3139f24d85d6dcd99",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_44fc242a5611aa06b35befea",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "role 属性帮助辅助技术解释一个标签代表哪种元素。默认情况下，  被视为一个列表，但我们即将添加的样式将改变它。添加 role 将恢复 ul 元素的“列表”含义。如果你想了解更多关于为什么要这样做，你可以看看 Scott O'Hara's article, \"Fixing Lists\".",
        "text_hash": "430cb6abdde1fe75c677092c0ce66f2d52b0a504347ceb915290cda2ee0e73e4",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_bc31d20681d5be8e77fffbfe",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "aria-labelledby 属性告诉辅助技术，我们把列表标题当作标签，用来描述它下面的列表的目的。这种关联能让列表包含更多信息，这可以帮助屏幕阅读器用户更好地理解它的目的。",
        "text_hash": "911c6750a097b098010eeb400afe84da09bc33ff7164f0bde10d518f68307a75",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_31d66933b8df4aae5d7e47c1",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "最后，我们列表项中的标签和输入有一些 JSX 特有的属性：",
        "text_hash": "24b0574e066ee88eece5697cb610841be98cfb894726f78b6fbf6addcf8e4b17",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_19c66f41170ad97e00715cc2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "html",
        "text_hash": "e5e239560bc125a20ff2ac1fea50915bc198dd4f5b5256ec447a8a71e00132b3",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_6f986fc35dfb3f31d63afd49",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "Eat",
        "text_hash": "ebecb9cef8f2103c8885e5732df330174d137867b033b179cefc94b1ea23bb6d",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_327bc3d8fd16416f30d8d3e4",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "标签中的 defaultChecked 属性告诉 React 最初要检查这个复选框。如果我们像在普通的 HTML 中那样使用 checked，React 会在浏览器控制台中记录一些与处理复选框事件有关的警告，这是我们不想要的。现在不用太担心这个问题——我们将在以后使用事件的时候讨论这个问题。",
        "text_hash": "e7c5a14aee3a5f58d376fb86f0c9c1dd76fcdd9d641f29d05c6d11b824923168",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_ac68c8679113a660ab47962e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "htmlFor 属性对应于 HTML 中使用的 for 属性。因为 for 是一个保留词，我们不能在 JSX 中使用 for 作为属性，所以 React 使用 htmlFor 代替。",
        "text_hash": "a8283011d7a4141a0e64c183aded1ef0b49d5700fbf91561b4fe381893e28bf2",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_72a9000a86460253134e494b",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "说明：",
        "text_hash": "3e633a204a634ff20472f885b6163e390c1012e02cb0456dbd990f52162ddb93",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_2d8a753ef56261f7a7db7106",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "要在 JSX 属性中使用布尔值（true 和 false），你必须用大括号把它们括起来。如果你写 defaultChecked=\"true\"，defaultChecked 的值将是 \"true\"——一个字符串字面。记住——这实际上是 JavaScript，而不是 HTML!\n在前面的代码片段中使用的 aria-pressed 属性的值是 \"true\"，因为 aria-pressed 不是像 checked 那样是一个真正的布尔属性。",
        "text_hash": "a03f6840ec0a12f9954c716334c09fced44f4aa1edc0d2ba788a3c1b41232c7a",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "unordered_list"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_27a11d878472a23be4884e77",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "实现样式",
        "text_hash": "72a0b8a7a79264dc300bc5d53153aa06fd2c0317639da5504198aa392468e021",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_86ee1cbe6bbfc6b98433cf1f",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "将下面的 CSS 代码粘贴到 src/index.css 中，使其取代当前的内容：",
        "text_hash": "7fe66932f1804b303f8e3f690066b0ee5429f2cd0bf68356ebc4ba36554327af",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_92efba6ed23be7cb03a887f2",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "css\n/* RESETS */\n*,\n*::before,\n*::after {\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n*:focus {\n  outline: 3px dashed #228bec;\n  outline-offset: 0;\n}\nhtml {\n  font: 62.5% / 1.15 sans-serif;\n}\nh1,\nh2 {\n  margin-bottom: 0;\n}\nul {\n  list-style: none;\n  padding: 0;\n}\nbutton {\n  border: none;\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  width: auto;\n  overflow: visible;\n  background: transparent;\n  color: inherit;\n  font: inherit;\n  line-height: normal;\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: inherit;\n  -moz-osx-font-smoothing: inherit;\n  -webkit-appearance: none;\n}\nbutton::-moz-focus-inner {\n  border: 0;\n}\nbutton,\ninput,\noptgroup,\nselect,\ntextarea {\n  font-family: inherit;\n  font-size: 100%;\n  line-height: 1.15;\n  margin: 0;\n}\nbutton,\ninput {\n  overflow: visible;\n}\ninput[type=\"text\"] {\n  border-radius: 0;\n}\nbody {\n  width: 100%;\n  max-width: 68rem;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  font:\n    1.6rem/1.25 Arial,\n    sans-serif;\n  background-color: #f5f5f5;\n  color: #4d4d4d;\n}\n@media screen and (min-width: 620px) {\n  body {\n    font-size: 1.9rem;\n    line-height: 1.31579;\n  }\n}\n/*END RESETS*/\n/* GLOBAL STYLES */\n.form-group > input[type=\"text\"] {\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin-top: 0.4rem;\n}\n.btn {\n  padding: 0.8rem 1rem 0.7rem;\n  border: 0.2rem solid #4d4d4d;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  text-transform: capitalize;\n}\n.btn.toggle-btn {\n  border-width: 1px;\n  border-color: #d3d3d3;\n}\n.btn.toggle-btn[aria-pressed=\"true\"] {\n  text-decoration: underline;\n  border-color: #4d4d4d;\n}\n.btn__danger {\n  color: #fff;\n  background-color: #ca3c3c;\n  border-color: #bd2130;\n}\n.btn__filter {\n  border-color: lightgrey;\n}\n.btn__primary {\n  color: #fff;\n  background-color: #000;\n}\n.btn-group {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n}\n.btn-group > * {\n  flex: 1 1 49%;\n}\n.btn-group > * + * {\n  margin-left: 0.8rem;\n}\n.label-wrapper {\n  margin: 0;\n  flex: 0 0 100%;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.visually-hidden {\n  position: absolute !important;\n  height: 1px;\n  width: 1px;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  clip: rect(1px 1px 1px 1px);\n  clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\n  white-space: nowrap;\n}\n[class*=\"stack\"] > * {\n  margin-top: 0;\n  margin-bottom: 0;\n}\n.stack-small > * + * {\n  margin-top: 1.25rem;\n}\n.stack-large > * + * {\n  margin-top: 2.5rem;\n}\n@media screen and (min-width: 550px) {\n  .stack-small > * + * {\n    margin-top: 1.4rem;\n  }\n  .stack-large > * + * {\n    margin-top: 2.8rem;\n  }\n}\n.stack-exception {\n  margin-top: 1.2rem;\n}\n/* END GLOBAL STYLES */\n.todoapp {\n  background: #fff;\n  margin: 2rem 0 4rem 0;\n  padding: 1rem;\n  position: relative;\n  box-shadow:\n    0 2px 4px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2),\n    0 2.5rem 5rem 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n}\n@media screen and (min-width: 550px) {\n  .todoapp {\n    padding: 4rem;\n  }\n}\n.todoapp > * {\n  max-width: 50rem;\n  margin-left: auto;\n  margin-right: auto;\n}\n.todoapp > form {\n  max-width: 100%;\n}\n.todoapp > h1 {\n  display: block;\n  max-width: 100%;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin: 0;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n.label__lg {\n  line-height: 1.01567;\n  font-weight: 300;\n  padding: 0.8rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n.input__lg {\n  padding: 2rem;\n  border: 2px solid #000;\n}\n.input__lg:focus {\n  border-color: #4d4d4d;\n  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px;\n}\n[class*=\"__lg\"] {\n  display: inline-block;\n  width: 100%;\n  font-size: 1.9rem;\n}\n[class*=\"__lg\"]:not(:last-child) {\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n@media screen and (min-width: 620px) {\n  [class*=\"__lg\"] {\n    font-size: 2.4rem;\n  }\n}\n.filters {\n  width: 100%;\n  margin: unset auto;\n}\n/* Todo item styles */\n.todo {\n  display: flex;\n  flex-direction: row;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n}\n.todo > * {\n  flex: 0 0 100%;\n}\n.todo-text {\n  width: 100%;\n  min-height: 4.4rem;\n  padding: 0.4rem 0.8rem;\n  border: 2px solid #565656;\n}\n.todo-text:focus {\n  box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 2px;\n}\n/* CHECKBOX STYLES */\n.c-cb {\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  font-weight: 400;\n  font-size: 1.6rem;\n  line-height: 1.25;\n  display: block;\n  position: relative;\n  min-height: 44px;\n  padding-left: 40px;\n  clear: left;\n}\n.c-cb > label::before,\n.c-cb > input[type=\"checkbox\"] {\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n  top: -2px;\n  left: -2px;\n  width: 44px;\n  height: 44px;\n}\n.c-cb > input[type=\"checkbox\"] {\n  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  position: absolute;\n  z-index: 1;\n  margin: 0;\n  opacity: 0;\n}\n.c-cb > label {\n  font-size: inherit;\n  font-family: inherit;\n  line-height: inherit;\n  display: inline-block;\n  margin-bottom: 0;\n  padding: 8px 15px 5px;\n  cursor: pointer;\n  touch-action: manipulation;\n}\n.c-cb > label::before {\n  content: \"\";\n  position: absolute;\n  border: 2px solid currentcolor;\n  background: transparent;\n}\n.c-cb > input[type=\"checkbox\"]:focus + label::before {\n  border-width: 4px;\n  outline: 3px dashed #228bec;\n}\n.c-cb > label::after {\n  box-sizing: content-box;\n  content: \"\";\n  position: absolute;\n  top: 11px;\n  left: 9px;\n  width: 18px;\n  height: 7px;\n  transform: rotate(-45deg);\n  border: solid;\n  border-width: 0 0 5px 5px;\n  border-top-color: transparent;\n  opacity: 0;\n  background: transparent;\n}\n.c-cb > input[type=\"checkbox\"]:checked + label::after {\n  opacity: 1;\n}",
        "text_hash": "d3c3e96051931d003cda60364cf9d1a1a2457039e499fd874d8be9bd3b87b979",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_3a0f96d89332dd1506c5904e",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "保存并刷新浏览器，你的应用程序现在应该有正常的样式。",
        "text_hash": "57d177cd48105b180d9591ba0b04493634067a33ea4a1d400bf6f9b20012e1af",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "paragraph"
    },
    {
      "target_block_id": "lrtb_521a8380b36a6dae896fdd76",
      "text": {
        "locale": "zh-Hans-CN",
        "qa_status": "passed",
        "text": "总结",
        "text_hash": "04830193b408eeb17c18cfb88440e68061423af6e0c2944c79e4c4cfc6a0f0dc",
        "variant_version_id": "lrzv_b0c8556cb5fc912283155b43"
      },
      "type": "heading"
    },
    {
